            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>特許通訊(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:CHTR:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/CHTR\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">CHTR-US</a>)截至台北時間17日01:01股價上漲11.08美元，報231.37美元，漲幅5.03%，成交量830,730（股），盤中最高價231.37美元、最低價220.54美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：-0.04%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：+0.04%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：+0.26%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：+0.79%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>特許通訊(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:CHTR:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/CHTR\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">CHTR-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：-0.6%</li> <li>近 1 月：+0.96%</li> <li>近 3 月：+13.2%</li> <li>近 6 月：-16.73%</li> <li>今年以來：+5.53%</li></ul></section></main>",
